reviewText:
If you love staring at disgusting women's boobs then this movie is for you.
Unfortunately the entire series is like this but this is the worst of them all.

Five women are topless only. Two have ugly fake breasts, the other three have beautiful real breasts. One gives a far away full frontal in a darkly lit room. Biggest negative is the sound starts 2-3 seconds before the peoples lips start moving.

I found this on the Vamps and Witches 4 movie set for about $5, so at $1.25 per movie I wasn't disappointed.  The story line was a bit odd as to the relationship with the snake creature that sucked the life out of the victims with a lightning beam of some sort... after the female vampire had their way with them first, both sexually and then blood draining.  The women were mostly good looking and the sex average for a softcore movie, the gore was on the light side.  Was true to form for the Witchcraft series with a simple plot and lots of flesh, worth a watch.
